#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int test;
    cin>>test;
    while(test--){
                  long long l1,l2,l;
                  long long b1,b2,b;
                  long long r1,r2,r;
                  long long t1,t2,t;
                  cin>>l1>>b1>>r1>>t1;
                  cin>>l2>>b2>>r2>>t2;
                  l=l1>l2?l1:l2;
                  b=b1>b2?b1:b2;
                  r=r1<r2?r1:r2;
                  t=t1<t2?t1:t2;
                  if(l>=r || b>=t)
                          cout<<"No Overlap"<<endl;
                  else
                          cout<<l<<" "<<b<<" "<<r<<" "<<t<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
